         80 x 5cm box segments, sitting 0.5mm above the white floor.
         contype/conaffinity=0: no physics collision, visual + sensor only.
         Platoon starts at x=0,-0.3,-0.6 all facing +X — line runs
         from x=-2.0 to x=+2.0 giving runway in both directions.
